    "markdown": "### 5. Amazon AWS (US) — LLM ✓ TTS ✓ STT ✓\n\n**Status:** Active.\n\n**Bedrock:** 15+ model providers. Amazon Nova series (Micro $0.035/MTok to Premier $2.50/MTok), plus Anthropic, Meta, Mistral, DeepSeek, MiniMax, Moonshot, OpenAI models. New accounts: $200 credits.\n\n**Polly TTS:** Standard: **$4/1M chars**, Neural: **$16/1M chars**, Generative: **$30/1M chars**, Long-Form: **$100/1M chars**. 100+ voices, 40+ languages. SSML support. Free tier (12 months): 5M standard + 1M neural chars/month.\n\n**Transcribe STT:** **$0.024/min** (Tier 1). 100+ languages. Real-time WebSocket streaming. Free tier (12 months): 60 min/month.",
